msgid "V4L2 device driver that doesn't require a media controller to be used."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/glossary.rst:209
msgid ""
"Such drivers have the ``V4L2_CAP_IO_MC`` device_caps field unset (see :ref:"
"`VIDIOC_QUERYCAP`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/glossary.rst:211
msgid "V4L2 Sub-device API"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../userspace-api/media/glossary.rst:213
msgid ""
"Part of the :term:`V4L2 API` which control :term:`V4L2 sub-devices <V4L2 Sub-"
"device>`, like sensors, HDMI receivers, scalers, deinterlacers."
